r than a human=E2=80=99s gut instinct for markets:</p><blockquote><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">RBC Bluebay Asset Management, for instance, relishes t=
he ability to hide sizable trades from other players by using algorithms th=
at =E2=80=98slice and dice=E2=80=99 their execution. ...</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s better for risk =E2=80=94 I want everyt=
hing to be less touched, less keyboards stroked,=E2=80=9D said Stuart Campb=
ell, who leads fixed income trading at the asset manager. =E2=80=9CIn the F=
