less and less need for me to pick up the phone to do a big block trade.=E2=
=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=C2=A0The =E2=80=9Cbuy =
quietly=E2=80=9D algorithm is apparently named Chameleon:</p><blockquote><p=
 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At BNP [Paribas SA], the three algorithms all ha=
